snippet.textDisplay: This is the thing about Kirby games. On the outside, they look like happy, cheerful and easygoing kids games. But on the inside, Kirby games can get DAMN intense and creepy when they want. One of the big contributing factors to this is the music. It really sets the gloomy and dark mood and atmosphere for the stage. I freakin' love it.
